{"tid":1443640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民意真係咁重要?","createTime":"2019-08-11T09:33:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T09:44:52.000Z","uid":266547,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d093b705a66769c714065b10008ae37e3303ec53","tid":1443640,"uid":266547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:33:54.000Z","msg":"到左而家呢步, 只要前線繼續行動, 一定會逼到英美出手, 港府跪低. <br />\n<br />\n&quot;但係<span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓社會</span> 會產生<span style=\"color: red;\">民怨</span> 失去<span style=\"color: red;\">民意支持</span>喎!&quot;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\nThe mass is irrelevant in a revolution, but relevant in election. If you care for the mass in a revolution, it means you are fighting for something else, something off the track.</span><br />\n<br />\n社會改革, 係唔需要大眾認同. 佢地加入/退出都唔可以阻到我地. <br />\n<br />\n咩人最關心所謂民意, 專叫前線冷靜唔好衝呢?  就係個啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">為求<span style=\"color: red;\">選票</span>既人</span>. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港加油 前線手足我撐你!</span>"},{"pid":"2e4997abe2f57ffa699b83c7eaea37c50ea87e9b","tid":1443640,"uid":262035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:39:02.000Z","msg":"都係嗰句<br />\n除非你已經諗住用武力推反政權<br />\n如果唔係你都係要夠政府回應同改革<br />\n咁樣就一定要有民意支持（二百萬和理非）<br />\n唔係既話政府睬你都傻<br />\n<br />\n政府最驚既係有大量和理非支持勇武"},{"pid":"9889d928af4f5169b25e632599857707f0fec7bb","tid":1443640,"uid":153824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:39:13.000Z","msg":"無民意邊有街坊落黎幫手，當六七咪無民意，啲人捐錢比差佬添，過分追求民意係on9，但唔等於民意係唔重要，膠都費事比"},{"pid":"71bdd0e213da29a8987b9528eade051acd9258ba","tid":1443640,"uid":180168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:44:52.000Z","msg":"社會改革, 係唔需要大眾認同<br />\n<br />\n你都on9<br />\n無大眾認同你點改革呀"}]}